    "long_instructions": "### DJ Ritmo loves effects and needs a dynamic beat!\r\nDJ Ritmo loves using effects in her music. Can you help her create a looping drum and bass line that will use different alternating filters?\r\n\r\n**Do this:**\r\n- Code a loop with a high delay for 2 measures, then no delay for 2 measures.\r\n- Make sure the backbeat plays for at least 10 measures.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
